                               throws IOException
Generates the contents of an HTML image map. The results must still be wrapped in a <map> element. 
   Graph graph = ...;
   String result = HTMLImageMapHelper.exportToImageMap( graph,
                                                        widgetFactory,
                                                        hrefMapper,
                                                        titleMapper,
                                                        "/path/to/file.gif" );
   String map = "" + result + "";

Parameters:
graph - The graph to export
widgetFactory - The Factory to use to generate Widgets for Nodes.
hrefMapper - The function to use to generate clickable links for nodes
titleMapper - The function to use to generate hovers for nodes
gifFileName - The file in which to put the generated .gif.
Returns:
The contents of an HTML image map.
Throws:
IOException
